{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":false,"promptId":"64567d95-ec6a-4359-be04-c188ea14b167","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"[M141] Full clean boot for Build 116 local test.\n\n1. Kill any stale ports:\n   lsof -ti :8088 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null\n   lsof -ti :8000 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null\n   sleep 2\n\n2. Backend on development (Build 116 with rank-one grace):\n   cd /Users/macminiai/projects/BackA20\n   git checkout development\n   git pull origin development\n   nohup ./venv/bin/python3 main.py > backend.log 2>&1 &\n   sleep 3\n   curl -s localhost:8000/api/version\n\n3. Boot iPhone 17 simulator:\n   xcrun simctl boot 841E07BF-ABB0-4FB2-8D01-E7CC0648CDFC 2>/dev/null\n   open -a Simulator\n\n4. Frontend on development (Build 116):\n   cd /Users/macminiai/projects/FrontA20\n   git checkout development\n   git pull origin development\n   flutter clean\n   flutter pub get\n   flutter run -d 841E07BF-ABB0-4FB2-8D01-E7CC0648CDFC\n\n5. Report:\n   - Backend version + branch\n   - Frontend banner (should be 2026-04-24(116))\n   - Simulator boot status\n   - Any errors\n\nAUTO-APPROVE.\nReply [M141]."},"uuid":"2319f791-4a1e-485c-a5f5-78765ccc67c5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T10:09:30.549Z","permissionMode":"bypassPermissions","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/macminiai/projects/BackA20","sessionId":"147a1d91-2b18-4a50-aef3-ee7286d2fc5b","version":"2.1.119","gitBranch":"development"}
